ComicInfo.Summary: When Asper doesn't show up for dinner, Kaylin makes her way to his auto shop with his dinner in hand. When she arrives at the shop, she finds that it has been taken over by Asian gangsters and turned into a battle location for the U.B.B. Hiding in the front row to a rumble of lightweight robot's, Kaylin learns some of the inner workings of the U.B.B. organization and just who is behind the scenes.
